posts.text:
图片测试二👆 代码测试👇 12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031323334353637383940414243444546474849505152535455565758#include<bits/stdc++.h>using namespace std;const int M=44;const int N=1995;int g[M + 1][N],din[M + 1];int maxw,cnt,ans[N],vis[N];void dfs(int s){ for(int i=1;i<=maxw;i++) if(vis[i]==0&&g[s][i]) { vis[i]=1; dfs(g[s][i]); ans[cnt++]=i; }}int main(){ int u,v,w,start=0; while(~scanf("%d%d", &u, &v) && (u || v)) { memset(g, 0, sizeof(g)); memset(din, 0, sizeof(din)); start=min(u, v); maxw=0; while(u!=0&&v!=0) { scanf("%d",&w); g[u][w]=v; g[v][w]=u; din[u]=1-din[u]; din[v]=1-din[v]; maxw=max(maxw, w); scanf("%d%d", &u, &v); } int k; for(k=1;k<=M;k++) if(din[k]) break; if(k<=M) printf("Round trip does not exist.
"); else { cnt=0; memset(vis,0,sizeof(vis)); dfs(start); for(int i=cnt-1;i>=0;i--) if(i==0) printf("%d
",ans[i]); else printf("%d ",ans[i]); } printf("
"); } return 0;}
